Test/Declarative version 0.01
=============================

Allows you to write tests in a more declarative style.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

        Test::More      =>  0.46,
        Test::Builder   =>  0.16,
        Set::CrossProduct   => 1.4,

